name: James D. SCHNELLER, Petitioner v. PROTHONOTARY OF the SUPREME COURT OF PENNSYLVANIA, Respondent

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 6th day of December, 2011, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus and the “Emergency Application for Temporary Restraining Order and Injunction” are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
